{"tid":2500924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung一季度銷量銳增32%，重回全球冠軍寶座，相反apple市佔率大跌！","createTime":"2021-04-23T04:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T05:18:24.000Z","uid":391580,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"60f5fea3ac305a02b4922b8973be198cf0f7657e","tid":2500924,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:23:06.000Z","msg":"據韓國《亞洲經濟》4月22日報道，市場調查機構Strategy Analytics統計顯示，三星電子今年一季度智能手機出貨量為7700萬部，同比銳增32%，占全球市場份額的23%，高居榜首；蘋果手機以5700萬部出貨量位居其後，雖同比大幅增長44%，但市場份額卻從上季度的21%降至17%。繼三星和蘋果之後，小米（4900萬部，15%）、OPPO（3800萬部，11%）、VIVO（3700萬部，11%）分列第3&mdash;5位。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，三星電子自2011年以來一直保持着20%以上的全球市場份額，去年第四季度降至17%，被蘋果反超。今年一季度，三星電子憑借Galaxy S21系列高端產品提前上市以及中低端產品銷售增長等利好，重回冠軍寶座。"},{"pid":"1fdc6b94cea5c2ca41fe889068b4097dc31f9d1d","tid":2500924,"uid":155095,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:25:52.000Z","msg":"Samsung加油，Android除咗Samsung，其它份額已經俾中國嘅小米，VIVO，OPPO佔據 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5224308a5e9a506e957b01880454150740d4a6d0","tid":2500924,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRPqzmtUX9b2kiFAUY4Lymd5cWTQsKbcM32qMFH74AJ8v?filename=Nw9dfer.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNw9dfer.gif&h=3c3c2223&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZpzECuHkVnMowYFnRkzY3q1u9AeCsARwaLsGLwXq5Q28?filename=fg5Px07.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffg5Px07.gif&h=8b60eee3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"087c1cec7c3e7fcf7cdd50d1ac8c175c9cba56a9","tid":2500924,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:29:44.000Z","msg":"Samsung有無後門？親唔親共？"},{"pid":"d31d3600812fdeb9f0273b2162a7048398ff47bb","tid":2500924,"uid":155095,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"087c1cec7c3e7fcf7cdd50d1ac8c175c9cba56a9","tid":2500924,"uid":